{"tid":57942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建立南粵國可行性研究","createTime":"2016-12-28T12:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T15:04:10.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c01a31f1a6b821f39370c605f96438f18a886c8f","tid":57942,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"如題，先無視支那會打擊建國，假設支那內亂無暇自固。<br />\n<br />\n港獨唔可行，因為除左錢，港口同法制，香港其實咩都冇，客觀條件要獨立唔可行。反而2廣合併，各司其職係可行嘅方案。<br />\n<br />\n就地理黎講，作為護國神山嘅南嶺，歷史上多次阻擋支那入侵。珠江流經2廣，水利資料豐富。<br />\n<br />\n就產業黎講，農業有廣西，工業有廣東，高科技有深圳，第三產業同港口對外有香港，配套完善。而且有咁多核電廠係本國，國防同能源都唔係問題。<br />\n<br />\n最重要一點，2廣人識廣東話佔多數，同文同種向心力自然高。<br />\n<br />\n對外，可以加入美國陣營，現時第一島鏈唔包南海，形成突出部，如果加入美帝，將會形成越南，南粵，台灣，日本嘅新島鏈，由美軍睇場。"},{"pid":"63a15fb2ce1172c2394eca58363890a7e9050d02","tid":57942,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又開膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5f9ba5c398b6740b470179db7603431ece7651","tid":57942,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母又開膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌個一鍵留名咁嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29ac9b5439e8c790f90657f39a2539476bf2ef5","tid":57942,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難啲囉<br />\n太多北佬喺南方"},{"pid":"cbb289942612a67a62580646ebddbb5490ae32ba","tid":57942,"uid":21533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"太多外省進佔左廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩地文化都有出入 雖然廣東好多人都識睇繁體字 因為cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ee608d1b82d9370c2a9c71ce3884d2ea4f76a3","tid":57942,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難啲囉<br />\n太多北佬喺南方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驅逐支那北佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔走就要種族清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bd3079d9c5f82655c986088787119c38e5e428","tid":57942,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太多外省進佔左廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩地文化都有出入 雖然廣東好多人都識睇繁體字 因為cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2廣文化同本地文化差異，小過大家同支那北佬嘅差異。<br />\n<br />\n講同一種話，讀寫同一種字已經係建國嘅一種優勢，代表大家更容易了解大家嘅價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acf9382ce3dfd294b5d90dd24d9daec1dcb885c","tid":57942,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"準備去深圳屠殺撈閪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98798776dfee1dcca42a5cdba84cdfe82cee2295","tid":57942,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"南粵建國，其實形勢一片大好。要守穩南嶺，關鍵唔係山而係長江流域，基本可分為上中下游3區，上游四川+重慶+貴洲，中游2湖，下遊長3角出海口，羈縻得好可以用佢地做肉盾，抵擋支那北佬進犯。<br />\n<br />\n而且3地共通點係屬於楚文化地區，其中四川好多人其實係閒未清初個陣由2湖個邊過去，湖廣填四川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a379136b9d1c9c52bfec437dfe606d238e5fe33","tid":57942,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"兩廣同香港文化歷史差異甚大，不可能統一，以保香港民族純正<br />\n但可以考慮係南粵國建立傀儡政權/殖民地/衛星國"},{"p